+# What is this directory?
+
+This directory is a copy of https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg/tree/1de2026f28ead93ff1773e6e680387643e914ea1/ports/orc
+with aditional patch appended to fix-cmake.patch. This diff ensures network isolation of the pipeline from non-trusted network resources.
+
+
+Additional information on vcpkg overlay ports: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/vcpkg/concepts/overlay-ports
+
+
+The ADO task "Visualizing orc overlay port dif" Visualizes the diff; example output:
+```
+C:\__w\1\s>git diff --no-index C:\__w\1\s\ci\vcpkg\overlayPorts\orc C:\usr\local\share\vcpkg\ports\orc 
+diff --git "a/C:\\__w\\1\\s\\ci\\vcpkg\\overlayPorts\\orc/fix-cmake.patch" "b/C:\\usr\\local\\share\\vcpkg\\ports\\orc/fix-cmake.patch"
+index 188e0a3..cabc118 100644
+--- "a/C:\\__w\\1\\s\\ci\\vcpkg\\overlayPorts\\orc/fix-cmake.patch"
++++ "b/C:\\usr\\local\\share\\vcpkg\\ports\\orc/fix-cmake.patch"
+@@ -142,20 +142,3 @@ index 3863c408..b71ab5ea 100644
+    ${CMAKE_THREAD_LIBS_INIT}
+    )
+  
+-diff --git a/cmake_modules/ThirdpartyToolchain.cmake b/cmake_modules/ThirdpartyToolchain.cmake
+-index aa520ff61..04c7a3ad4 100644
+---- a/cmake_modules/ThirdpartyToolchain.cmake
+-+++ b/cmake_modules/ThirdpartyToolchain.cmake
+-@@ -72,8 +72,9 @@ endif ()
