+After that there are 2 options to download the package:
+1. Integrate terrapin command into toolchain (documentaion see above)
+2. Use URL directly: https://vcpkg.storage.devpackages.microsoft.io/artifacts/f3ea69ffa2b525d5dcc01ff44113dc18b08733d315d750d8146da66f3be21772c0676972ef877a88abbf9309ad92e1f92144028f488470a4e89eda9c2308886a
